(1924, 137, 'section-2_last_row', '&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<p class=\"question\">Order fulfillment features: professional shipping documents (packing slips and shipping labels)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pt-25\">Save time with these automated shipping documents. You can easily create packing slips and shipping labels directly from your sales orders, and print them to attach them to your delivery packages.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pt-25\">The packing slip is a shipping document that accompanies each package, which includes a detailed list of the packages contents. This makes it easy for you to pick, pack and ship your orders at record speed. They are also super useful for your customers to manage receiving and acceptance of your orders.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pt-25\">And shipping labels come handy too. No more worrying about your teams handwriting  with TradeSystems integrated fulfillment shipping tools you can quickly batch print your shipping labels your transport carrier will love you for this!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
