(5836, 91, '_section-1_french', 'field_5cfaf6d8d6c16'),
(5837, 91, 'section-2_fench_content', '<h3 class=\"pt-3\">Processing</h3>\r\n<p class=\"question\">SYNCHRONIZE YOUR ORDERS WITH YOUR INVENTORY</p>\r\nCustomer satisfaction is key to succeeding in this increasingly competitive marketplace, where selling world-class products is meaningless without a good order management software\r\n<p class=\"question\">SALES ORDERS WORKFLOW - FROM ORDER CREATION TO FULFILLMENT:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li>Draft (send &amp; edit sales quotes)</li>\r\n 	<li>Active (mark committed stock, receive payments)</li>\r\n 	<li>Finalized (email invoice, mark orders as paid/unpaid, fulfilled or part fulfilled)</li>\r\n 	<li>Fulfilled (mark that all goods have been shipped, mark the order as paid/ unpaid)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"question\">Fulfill more orders effortlessly</p>\r\nOUR SOFTWARE ENABLES YOU TO AUTOMATE AND CONTROL YOUR ORDER FULFILLMENT,\r\nINTEGRATE ALL THE CHANNELS, LOCATIONS AND PROCESSES, EXECUTE EACH STEP NEEDED IN THE WORKFLOW, AND HAVE VISIBILITY OF THE ENTIRE PROCESS.'),
(5838, 91, '_section-2_fench_content', 'field_5cfaf75cd6c1a'),
(5839, 91, 'section-2_fench_image', '129'),
(5840, 91, '_section-2_fench_image', 'field_5cfaf75cd6c1b'),
(5841, 91, 'section-2_fench_last_row', '&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<p class=\"question\">Order fulfillment features: professional shipping documents (packing slips and shipping labels)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pt-25\">Save time with these automated shipping documents. You can easily create packing slips and shipping labels directly from your sales orders, and print them to attach them to your delivery packages.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pt-25\">The packing slip is a shipping document that accompanies each package, which includes a detailed list of the packages contents. This makes it easy for you to pick, pack and ship your orders at record speed. They are also super useful for your customers to manage receiving and acceptance of your orders.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-3\">\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pt-25\">And shipping labels come handy too. No more worrying about your teams handwriting  with TradeSystems integrated fulfillment shipping tools you can quickly batch print your shipping labels your transport carrier will love you for this!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
(5842, 91, '_section-2_fench_last_row', 'field_5cfaf75cd6c1c'),
