(5854, 91, '_section-4_french_image', 'field_5cfaf7a0d6c22'),
(5855, 91, 'section-4_french_last_row', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-12\">\r\n<ul class=\"answer-list\">\r\n 	<li class=\"pt-25\">CUSTOMER RETURNS? DAMAGED SHIPMENTS? O PROBLEM\r\nReturns can be time consuming and frustrating for both ou and your customers. Our easy shipping return ervices with free return labels take the worry out ofreturns. TradeSystem makes it easy to handle manage your customers returns by providing several tools &amp; services to ease the transaction. With flexible options to match your return policy, our warehouses can receive, process, &amp; restock the items into your inventory.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
